ColourPicker_UpdateDialogue (&47704)
#Parent ColourPicker_
#Prefix ColourPicker_
=>	R0 =	<flags=>.flags>
	R1 =	dialogue handle
	R2 =	<colour picker block=>colourpicker_block>

This call updates some or all contents of the colour picker whose handle is given.
#subpage flags
ColourPicker_UpdateDialogue Flags
Bit	Part of dialogue to update when set
#Line
0	whether the dialogue has a None button
1	whether the None button is selected
2	where <Message_ColourPickerColourChanged=>Msg_47701> is issued for
3	the visible area
4	reserved (must be 0)
5	the window title
6	colour setting
7	the colour model and setting (including optional data)
8	whether the dialogue ignores <Message_HelpRequest=>Msg_502>
9	whether the dialogue passes on unhandled keypresses